Never fear shadows. They simply mean there’s a light shining nearby.

Just like every night has its dawn
Just like every cowboy sings his sad, sad song

celebrating all the small wins on this journey, one day at a time 🤗 

What are the dreams you’d like to accomplish?
How disciplined and consistent are you everyday? 
How determined are you to accomplish your goals?
What drives you to continue on your journey?

Pre-run jam 🏃🏼‍♀️
‘You have been dying since the day you were born’ 🫡
Is today really August? Or are Julying to me? 🍉☀️⛱️
If you find a path with no obstacles, most likely it doesn’t lead anywhere. Make rock bottom the solid foundation in which you can rebuild yourself.
Optimism and inspiration come from within yourself 🖤
Sushi by Scratch in Coconut Grove ✨
Happy Sunday ✨ Always be the most fabulous, unhinged version of yourself 💁🏼‍♀️
